UBS Cancer Fund Shows Power of Impact Investing
A new oncology fund will finance academic research and access to cancer care in developing countries. 


 







By

Abby Schultz

 Biography




 




April 29, 2016


  UBS Wealth Management is proving investors in Asia will warm to funding projects with social and environmental benefits if the potential returns deliver. Earlier this week UBS closed the $471 million UBS Oncology Impact Fund, a vehicle aimed...
	      




 


