UBS Oncology Impact Fund Key Developments

MPM Capital Appoints William (Bill) C. Hahn to its Oncology Impact Fund Advisory Board
Jun 13 17
MPM Capital announced that William (Bill) C. Hahn will join its Oncology Impact Fund (OIF) Advisory Board. As a member of the OIF Advisory Board, Dr. Hahn will provide expert advice to support MPM’s strategy to build companies that seek to find cures for cancer. Dr. Hahn serves as a medical oncologist and Professor at Dana-Farber Cancer Institute and Harvard Medical School and is an Institute Member of the Broad Institute of MIT and Harvard. He is also the Chief Research Strategy Officer and the Chief of the Division of Molecular and Cellular Oncology in the Department of Medical Oncology at Dana-Farber Cancer Institute.


